The TurnDial Google Chrome Extension seamlessly connects your phone system to Chrome for features like click to call and screen pops. 

With the TurnDial extension, simply click on a phone number in any application and the TurnDial extension will automatically place a call. Along with click to call, the TurnDial extension offers CRM integration via screen pops.
